==============================================================================
bin/enable_mods

add ability to enable and disable mods at the same time
  enable_mods -mod2 +mod3 mod4
  will disable mod2 and enable mod3 and mod4

  enable_mods all -mod2
  will enable all mods except for mod2

add enable mods functions to array for 'all' option

change the way individual mods are enabled , probably using array for all option

==============================================================================
mcbuild
https://github.com/broese/mcbuild.git (or the projects directory)

Use mcbuild to automate:
  clear ground cover over colony territory
  place torches in low light areas
  assist miner (in minecolonies) with shafts
  feeding animals
  moving items from chest to chest

  what else?
